{"tid":1967831,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"同bf上床，但未開始搞野，佢已經嬲左我","createTime":"2020-04-11T08:04:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-12T12:46:29.000Z","uid":35361,"like":5,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"4f9ab30c238673fcc3e692cfb27067e500455b21","tid":1967831,"uid":35361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T08:04:35.000Z","msg":"早幾日去左男朋友屋企 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁佢屋企冇人, 緊係要大戰連場啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家好快手就除哂衫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你又摷下我, 我又咀下你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁大家都摷到high哂, 佢又扯到恆哂 準備埋牙之制 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁佢諗住入我先, 但我當時話 : 我依家都硬哂喎, 次次都係你入先, 不如今次我入你先 比我出一獲先啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢即時黑面話我唔理佢感受, 只顧自己出野 果晚大家不歡而散 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實大家都扯到硬哂, 邊個入先會好D?? <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc303cd65eb28e30be0fd73df4bae66ac8265eb0","tid":1967831,"uid":311223,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T08:05:44.000Z","msg":"This thread is <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">GAY</span></span>"},{"pid":"e18f75982763d928d4e530af4e40c17cd987817f","tid":1967831,"uid":140335,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T08:05:47.000Z","msg":"大